rianism, Mussolini’s Decennale broadens our understanding of fascist ideology, cultural politics, and Realpolitik.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Aug 2021) 0aFascism and culturezItalyxHistoryy20th century. 0aFascismzItalyxHistoryy20th century. 7aHISTORY / Europe / Italy.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of Toronto Press Complete eBook-Package 2014-2015z978311060681240uhttps://doi.org/10.3138/978144266411140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781442664111423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9781442664111.jpg  a978-3-11-060681-2  University of Toronto Press Complete eBook-Package 2014-2015c2014d2015  aGBV-deGruyter-alles